SUMMARY:From Idea to Intelligent Agent: Build\, Debug & Deploy AI Experien
 ces Fast in VS 
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nWhat if you could go from a spark o
 f an idea to a fully working AI agent—complete with reasoning workflows\
 , evaluation\, and deployment—in the same place you write your code? Wit
 h the AI Toolkit and Microsoft Foundry extension for VS Code\, that’s no
 w real.\n\nIn this session\, we’ll walk through an end‑to‑end develo
 per experience that makes AI development feel intuitive\, visual\, and inc
 redibly fast: explore cutting‑edge models\, generate and refine agents w
 ith GitHub Copilot\, visualize and debug complex workflows\, replay agent 
 events to pinpoint issues instantly\, evaluate quality with built‑in too
 ls\, and deploy directly to Foundry—all without ever leaving VS Code.\n\
 nIf you’re building AI apps or agentic systems\, this talk will show you
  how to turn your ideas into intelligent\, production‑ready experiences 
 with surprising speed and confidence.\n\n[Check out the workshop!](https:/
 /aka.ms/AIToolkit/workshop)\n\n📌 This session is a part of a series! [L
 earn more here](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1625/?wt.
 mc_id=meetup_S-1625_webpage_reactor)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/microsoft-reactor-toronto/events/3132
 42542/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260206T205453Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260206T205453Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
