SUMMARY:The 9 FabCon + SQLCon Takeaways the Community Is Talking About
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nWhat really stood out at FabCon and
  SQLCon once the sessions wrapped and everyone headed home?\n\nIn this ses
 sion\, Microsoft MVPs and community creators share the nine takeaways that
  stuck with them most.\n\nFrom standout announcements and practical lesson
 s to unexpected insights and hallway-conversation gems\, this is a fast-pa
 ced\, experience-driven recap focused on what you can actually use.\n\nWhe
 ther you attended or not\, you will hear what resonated most from the peop
 le who were there and shaping the conversation.
