SUMMARY:Model Mondays - Unlocking enterprise value with Cohere+ GitHub Age
 ntic Workflows
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nPartner Spotlight: Cohere joins Mod
 el Mondays to show how their cutting-edge AI models accelerate decision-ma
 king\, improve efficiency\, and drive enterprise value. This hands-on sess
 ion will feature a live demo and real-world use cases to help you work sma
 rter.\n\nTech Spotlight: Join lead maintainer Peli de Halleux as he demons
 trates GitHub Agentic Workflows and shows how to automate GitHub tasks usi
 ng AI agents with plain English instructions. Learn about the technology\,
  explore key features\, and see real-world examples of AI-powered GitHub a
 utomation.\n\n----------------------------------------------\n[Explore the
  repo](https://github.com/microsoft/model-mondays/blob/main/docs/model-mon
 days/2026-04-06-s03-e16.md)\n\n📢 [Join the conversation on Discord!](ht
 tps://aka.ms/model-mondays/discord)\n\n📌 This session is a part of the 
 Model Mondays series. [Learn more here!](https://developer.microsoft.com/r
 eactor/series/S-1485/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1485_webpage_reactor)
